{"tid":1854910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府仲可以出咩招謀害港人","createTime":"2020-01-31T18:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T18:21:49.000Z","uid":117332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19aa23144f9e7baaee9e25262473dd6f16452bc5","tid":1854910,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"政府係抗疫行動上已經唔止不作為，而係存心加劇疫情。<br />\n<br />\n例如，唔封關仲免費醫武漢病人。<br />\n唔分配口罩不突止仲截哂啲口罩入口，市場同政府都唔比你拎到口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下政府既下限可以去到邊。<br />\n1。由得口罩供應短缺，唔帶口罩要罰錢<br />\n2。後生仔係公開場合要遵守禁蒙面法<br />\n3。搵警察強迫醫護開工，但乜裝備都唔比醫護，迫佢地送死"},{"pid":"9e7c36f329dde57cd84b616cfaf9381fcf9ab7b6","tid":1854910,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"唔俾整口罩"},{"pid":"d01d906f5f7b6bbfc9ad90bc8dc1b6b1ddc61e14","tid":1854910,"uid":331814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，其實港共未算去到最盡，反正都開始唔理個市，玩緊急法已經大把野玩"},{"pid":"ca6a742aa9224a08af8d32f8059782f562f3ac0a","tid":1854910,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭幾時死"},{"pid":"dd1b333329499a25b2a01ad215e523401aa116da","tid":1854910,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"咁睇小港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}